race.comment: REBORN HOSTILITY (2) turned in a plain effort last time when fifth at this track over 720m behind Vodka And Ice (43.02) in a NG. Was in the money prior to that. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Key runner on her best form. MAGPIE HECTOR (3) is having his first run over this longer distance. Missed the frame last time when 4th and beaten 5 lengths (34.51) at The Meadows. Makes strong appeal on best. DERRY (7) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (43.00) last time in a NG at this track. Can measure up this time. BOUND'S MISSILE (4) collected a minor prize last start and must be considered.
